ygData.messageBody:
The gate spell is sold in the temple of life in Qeynos. you shouldnt be kos in
there unless you have been killing human npc's.
As a human necromancer who started in Qeynos most merchants will sell to me
and I have only found 2 npc's in the city that kos me.
Trinnes necromancer of the fith circle
